    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. This beauty has been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure. It's got plenty of life left in it and looks great inside and out. I've absolutely loved driving it, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and find this ride a great new home!",
