    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis maintains its balanced 50/50 weight distribution, supported by a factory limited-slip differential and reinforced subframe mounting points. Critical maintenance is current, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rod bearing service, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates flawlessly up to the 8,000 RPM redline. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and suspension damping remain tight and responsive. A mechanically sound, driver-focused example of BMW\u2019s M-division peak.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
