      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard. It offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical precision and a well-preserved aesthetic. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-performance asset that has been cared for with diligence. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 34900.0,
