    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a treat to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner immediately! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car is super dependable and drives like a dream. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
