      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically sound with documented VANOS servicing and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, while the variable M differential lock provides exceptional mechanical grip. An honest driver\u2019s car for the purist seeking high-revving atmospheric performance.",
